    {
      "title": "Legend",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 7 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "| Panel | Meaning |\n|---|---|\n| **Container Alive** | Searcher process is running |\n| **Container CPU < 80%** | 15m avg CPU under 80% |\n| **OOM Kills** | System-wide OOM kill counter (0 = healthy) |\n| **Root Disk > 10% Free** | Root filesystem has >10% available |\n| **Persistent Disk > 128GB Free** | Persistent volume has >128GB available |\n| **Network Up** | Non-loopback traffic detected in last 5m |\n\n\u2705 healthy · \u26a0\ufe0f unhealthy · \u2753 no data · OOM Kills shows the count"
